net/dst: Utility functions to build dst_metadata without supplying an skb

Extract __ip_tun_set_dst() and __ipv6_tun_set_dst() out of
ip_tun_rx_dst() and ipv6_tun_rx_dst(), to be used without supplying an
skb.

